        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "chore: fix esbuild production audit failure",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- update the root esbuild pin from 0.28.0 to 0.28.1, the first patched version for GHSA-gv7w-rqvm-qjhr\n- add an exact pnpm override so transitive consumers such as tsx resolve to esbuild 0.28.1 instead of the stale 0.28.0 lock snapshot\n- add version-scoped minimumReleaseAge exclusions for esbuild 0.28.1 and its matching @esbuild platform packages so the security patch can resolve before the normal 48-hour maturity window\n\n## Verification\n\n- node scripts/pre-commit/pnpm-audit-prod.mjs --audit-level=high\n- node --input-type=module -e 'import {readFile} from \"node:fs/promises\"; import {collectProdResolvedPackagesFromLockfile} from \"./scripts/pre-commit/pnpm-audit-prod.mjs\"; const versions = collectProdResolvedPackagesFromLockfile(await readFile(\"pnpm-lock.yaml\", \"utf8\")); console.log(JSON.stringify({esbuild:[...(versions.get(\"esbuild\") ?? [])]}, null, 2));'\n- pnpm install --lockfile-only --frozen-lockfile --ignore-scripts\n- pnpm exec esbuild --version\n- pnpm exec tsx --version\n- pnpm changed:lanes --json\n- pnpm deps:shrinkwrap:root:check\n- pnpm deps:root-ownership:check\n- git diff --check\n- pnpm build\n- .agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --prompt 'Review the scoped dependency security fix for GHSA-gv7w-rqvm-qjhr. Diff should only update esbuild to 0.28.1, keep pnpm release-age bypass narrowly scoped, and preserve lock/shrinkwrap/build/audit behavior.'\n\n## Notes\n\nObserved while investigating PR #91484 security-fast at head 39fd11f0bd. That PR has no dependency file changes; the same audit failed on current origin/main before this fix.\n\nProvenance: PR #87162 first added the root esbuild 0.28.0 pin. PR #88814 later carried that package/lock state forward. The CI failure was made visible when GitHub published GHSA-gv7w-rqvm-qjhr on 2026-06-12 with vulnerable range >=0.17.0 <0.28.1.\n",
